Description

A basic digital clock displaying hours, minutes, seconds, and AM/PM. This project utilizes Tkinter for a clean GUI and Python's time module for accurate timekeeping.

Features

- Displays current time in HH:MM:SS AM/PM format
- Updates every second for real-time accuracy
- Customizable font, color, and background
- Lightweight and easy to run

Requirements

- Python 3.x
- Tkinter library
